---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import ShapeFooter from "../../components/ShapeFooter.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="NocoBase Partner Program - Grow Your Business with NocoBase"
  description="Join the NocoBase Partner Program. Earn up to 40% commission on channel sales and keep 100% of your service revenue. Two flexible models designed for system integrators, consultants, and technology service providers."
  keywords="NocoBase partner, Partner Program, channel partner, service partner, reseller, system integrator"
>
  <!-- Hero/Banner Start -->
  <section class="bg-half-170 bg-light d-table w-100">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-10 text-center">
          <div class="title-heading">
            <span class="badge bg-soft-primary mb-3">Partner Program</span>
            <h1 class="fw-bold mt-2 mb-3">Grow Your Business<br/>with NocoBase</h1>
            <p class="para-desc mx-auto text-muted">Two flexible partnership models that let you earn up to 40% channel commission and keep 100% of your service revenue. Whether you focus on distribution, implementation, or both -- we grow together.</p>
            <div class="mt-4 pt-2">
              <a href="mailto:partner@nocobase.com" class="btn btn-primary me-3">
                <i class="uil uil-envelope me-1"></i>Contact Us
              </a>
              <a href="#partnership-models" class="btn btn-outline-primary">
                <i class="uil uil-arrow-down me-1"></i>Learn More
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->
      </div><!--end row-->
    </div><!--end container-->
  </section><!--end section-->
  <!-- Hero/Banner End -->

  <!-- Partnership Models Start -->
  <section class="section" id="partnership-models">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-12">
          <div class="section-title text-center mb-4 pb-2">
            <h4 class="title mb-4">Two Flexible Partnership Models</h4>
            <p class="para-desc mx-auto text-muted mb-0">Choose one model or combine both to maximize your revenue</p>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->
      </div><!--end row-->

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2">
          <div class="card border-0 shadow rounded h-100 p-4">
            <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
              <div class="icons text-start me-3">
                <i class="uil uil-store rounded h3 mb-0 text-primary"></i>
              </div>
              <h5 class="mb-0">Channel Distribution</h5>
            </div>
            <p class="text-muted">Promote and sell NocoBase products to earn tiered commissions based on your lifetime cumulative sales.</p>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
              <li class="d-flex align-items-start mb-3">
                <i class="uil uil-arrow-right text-primary me-2"></i>
                <span><strong>15% - 40%</strong> tiered commission rate</span>
              </li>
              <li class="d-flex align-items-start mb-3">
                <i class="uil uil-arrow-right text-primary me-2"></i>
                <span>Lifetime accumulation, no time limits</span>
              </li>
              <li class="d-flex align-items-start mb-3">
                <i class="uil uil-arrow-right text-primary me-2"></i>
                <span>Commissions only go up, never decrease</span>
              </li>
              <li class="d-flex align-items-start mb-0">
                <i class="uil uil-arrow-right text-primary me-2"></i>
                <span>Sales enablement materials provided</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->

        <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2">
          <div class="card border-0 shadow rounded h-100 p-4">
            <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
              <div class="icons text-start me-3">
                <i class="uil uil-setting rounded h3 mb-0 text-primary"></i>
              </div>
              <h5 class="mb-0">Service Implementation</h5>
            </div>
            <p class="text-muted">Provide deployment, customization, integration, and training services to earn project-based revenue.</p>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
              <li class="d-flex align-items-start mb-3">
                <i class="uil uil-arrow-right text-primary me-2"></i>
                <span>Keep <strong>100%</strong> of service revenue -- no fees to NocoBase</span>
              </li>
              <li class="d-flex align-items-start mb-3">
                <i class="uil uil-arrow-right text-primary me-2"></i>
                <span>Set your own pricing for services</span>
              </li>
              <li class="d-flex align-items-start mb-3">
                <i class="uil uil-arrow-right text-primary me-2"></i>
                <span>Tier up based on delivered project count</span>
              </li>
              <li class="d-flex align-items-start mb-0">
                <i class="uil uil-arrow-right text-primary me-2"></i>
                <span>Priority lead referrals at higher tiers</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->
      </div><!--end row-->
    </div><!--end container-->
  </section><!--end section-->
  <!-- Partnership Models End -->

  <!-- Why Partner Start -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-12">
          <div class="section-title text-center mb-4 pb-2">
            <h4 class="title mb-4">Why Partner with NocoBase</h4>
            <p class="para-desc mx-auto text-muted mb-0">A product built for high-value projects with strong partner economics</p>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->
      </div><!--end row-->

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2">
          <div class="card border-0 features feature-primary feature-clean course-feature p-4 overflow-hidden shadow h-100">
            <div class="icons text-start">
              <i class="uil uil-database rounded h3 mb-0"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body p-0 mt-4">
              <h5 class="title text-dark">Data Model-Driven</h5>
              <p class="text-muted mt-2">Supports complex business logic with a high project ceiling. Ideal for large enterprise contracts.</p>
              <i class="uil uil-database full-img"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->

        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2">
          <div class="card border-0 features feature-primary feature-clean course-feature p-4 overflow-hidden shadow h-100">
            <div class="icons text-start">
              <i class="uil uil-cube rounded h3 mb-0"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body p-0 mt-4">
              <h5 class="title text-dark">Plugin-Based Architecture</h5>
              <p class="text-muted mt-2">Highly customizable with large service space. Deep customization drives high-margin service revenue.</p>
              <i class="uil uil-cube full-img"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->

        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2">
          <div class="card border-0 features feature-primary feature-clean course-feature p-4 overflow-hidden shadow h-100">
            <div class="icons text-start">
              <i class="uil uil-lock-open-alt rounded h3 mb-0"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body p-0 mt-4">
              <h5 class="title text-dark">Open Source Transparency</h5>
              <p class="text-muted mt-2">Fully open code with no barriers to deep customization. Low technical risk builds client confidence.</p>
              <i class="uil uil-lock-open-alt full-img"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->

        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2">
          <div class="card border-0 features feature-primary feature-clean course-feature p-4 overflow-hidden shadow h-100">
            <div class="icons text-start">
              <i class="uil uil-dollar-sign rounded h3 mb-0"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body p-0 mt-4">
              <h5 class="title text-dark">One-Time Licensing</h5>
              <p class="text-muted mt-2">Unlimited users and applications. Controllable costs make it easy to close deals.</p>
              <i class="uil uil-dollar-sign full-img"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->

        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2">
          <div class="card border-0 features feature-primary feature-clean course-feature p-4 overflow-hidden shadow h-100">
            <div class="icons text-start">
              <i class="uil uil-robot rounded h3 mb-0"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body p-0 mt-4">
              <h5 class="title text-dark">AI Native</h5>
              <p class="text-muted mt-2">Integrated AI capabilities that align with enterprise AI adoption trends. A compelling differentiator.</p>
              <i class="uil uil-robot full-img"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->

        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2">
          <div class="card border-0 features feature-primary feature-clean course-feature p-4 overflow-hidden shadow h-100">
            <div class="icons text-start">
              <i class="uil uil-shield-check rounded h3 mb-0"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body p-0 mt-4">
              <h5 class="title text-dark">Full Data Sovereignty</h5>
              <p class="text-muted mt-2">Self-hosted deployment with complete control over code and data. Meets enterprise security requirements.</p>
              <i class="uil uil-shield-check full-img"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->
      </div><!--end row-->
    </div><!--end container-->
  </section><!--end section-->
  <!-- Why Partner End -->

  <!-- Partner Support Start -->
  <section class="section bg-light">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-12">
          <div class="section-title text-center mb-4 pb-2">
            <h4 class="title mb-4">How We Support You</h4>
            <p class="para-desc mx-auto text-muted mb-0">Comprehensive resources and support to help you succeed</p>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->
      </div><!--end row-->

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2">
          <div class="card border-0 text-center features feature-clean course-feature p-4 shadow h-100">
            <div class="icons text-center">
              <i class="uil uil-file-alt h1 text-primary"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="content mt-4">
              <h5>Sales Enablement</h5>
              <p class="text-muted mt-2">Sales materials, brochures, case studies, and competitive analysis materials</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->

        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2">
          <div class="card border-0 text-center features feature-clean course-feature p-4 shadow h-100">
            <div class="icons text-center">
              <i class="uil uil-headphones h1 text-primary"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="content mt-4">
              <h5>Technical Support</h5>
              <p class="text-muted mt-2">Dedicated support channels with priority response for higher-tier partners</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->

        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2">
          <div class="card border-0 text-center features feature-clean course-feature p-4 shadow h-100">
            <div class="icons text-center">
              <i class="uil uil-users-alt h1 text-primary"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="content mt-4">
              <h5>Lead Referrals</h5>
              <p class="text-muted mt-2">Customer referrals from NocoBase with priority access for certified partners</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->

        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2">
          <div class="card border-0 text-center features feature-clean course-feature p-4 shadow h-100">
            <div class="icons text-center">
              <i class="uil uil-award h1 text-primary"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="content mt-4">
              <h5>Brand Authorization</h5>
              <p class="text-muted mt-2">Official partner certificate, logo usage rights, and co-marketing opportunities</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->
      </div><!--end row-->
    </div><!--end container-->
  </section><!--end section-->
  <!-- Partner Support End -->

  <!-- CTA Section Start -->
  <section class="section bg-light">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-12 text-center">
          <h4 class="title mb-4">Ready to Become a Partner?</h4>
          <p class="text-muted para-desc mx-auto mb-4">
            Join a growing ecosystem of technology partners building on NocoBase. Whether you are a system integrator, consultant, or technology service provider, there is a place for you.
          </p>
        </div><!--end col-->
      </div><!--end row-->
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-10">
          <div class="card border-0 shadow rounded overflow-hidden">
            <iframe
              src="https://service-en.nocobase.com/public-forms/rl8c0cnkyzx"
              style="width: 100%; min-height: 700px; border: none;"
              loading="lazy"
            ></iframe>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->
      </div><!--end row-->
    </div><!--end container-->
  </section><!--end section-->
  <!-- CTA Section End -->

  <!-- FAQ Start -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-12">
          <div class="section-title text-center mb-4 pb-2">
            <h4 class="title mb-4">FAQ</h4>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->
      </div><!--end row-->

      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-10">
          <div class="accordion" id="partnerFaq">
            <div class="accordion-item border rounded shadow mb-3">
              <h2 class="accordion-header">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq1">
                  Are there any requirements to become a NocoBase partner?
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div id="faq1" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#partnerFaq">
                <div class="accordion-body text-muted">
                  <p>We evaluate each partner application based on background and capabilities. As long as the overall fit is right, you are welcome to join the partner program.</p>
                  <p>There are no additional barriers, no franchise fees, and no deposits required.</p>
                  <p class="mb-1">Two specific rules to be aware of:</p>
                  <ul>
                    <li class="mb-2"><strong>No discount on self-purchased licenses.</strong> When partners purchase licenses under their own name, standard official pricing applies.</li>
                    <li class="mb-2"><strong>First-order rule for Standard/Community edition distribution.</strong> To prevent arbitrage, the first order of Standard or Community edition license distribution only counts toward cumulative sales for tier advancement, but does not generate commission. Professional edition and above are not subject to this restriction and earn commission normally.</li>
                  </ul>
                  <p class="mb-0">We believe transparent, clear rules are essential to ensuring long-term fairness and sustainable growth across the ecosystem.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="accordion-item border rounded shadow mb-3">
              <h2 class="accordion-header">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq2">
                  Can I white-label NocoBase for distribution?
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div id="faq2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#partnerFaq">
                <div class="accordion-body text-muted">
                  <p>We do not support white-labeling.</p>
                  <p>We are committed to building a unified and long-term sustainable brand. A consistent brand helps establish clear, stable market recognition globally and strengthens customer trust in the product itself.</p>
                  <p>For partners, this brand consistency is equally important -- it provides stronger market endorsement and credibility, making the partnership more transparent, stable, and sustainable.</p>
                  <p class="mb-0">Partners may use the "NocoBase Partner" title and officially authorized brand materials for marketing, but repackaging or distributing the product under a white-label is not supported.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->
      </div><!--end row-->
    </div><!--end container-->
  </section><!--end section-->
  <!-- FAQ End -->

  <ShapeFooter />
</Layout>
